{"word":"H7835 - שָׁחַר - shâchar - shaw-khar' - Be black - கருப்பாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁחַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâchar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-khar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be black / கருப்பாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கறுத்துப்போ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be black; (Qal) to be black (used of skin)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (rather identical with <a href=\"#/H7836 - שָׁחַר - shâchar - shaw-khar'/7836\">H7836</a> through the idea of the <i>duskiness</i> of early dawn); to be <i>dim</i> or dark (in color): - be black."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7815 - שְׁחֹור - shᵉchôwr - shekh-ore'/7815\">H7815</a>, <a href=\"#/H7835 - שָׁחַר - shâchar - shaw-khar'/7835\">H7835</a>, <a href=\"#/H7838 - שָׁחֹר - shâchôr - shaw-khore'/7838\">H7838</a>, <a href=\"#/H7839 - שַׁחֲרוּת - shachărûwth - shakh-ar-ooth'/7839\">H7839</a>, <a href=\"#/H7840 - שְׁחַרְחֹרֶת - shᵉcharchôreth - shekh-ar-kho'-reth/7840\">H7840</a>, <a href=\"#/H806 - אַשְׁחוּר - ʼAshchûwr - ash-khoor'/806\">H806</a>"}]}